<i>(tripping</i> OSWALD<i>)</i> Or tripped, you lowlife <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tooltip-link"><span class="tooltip-css tooltip-background"><h4 class="semi-bold">football</h4><p>Football (soccer) was considered a lower-class game.</p></span>football</a> player?
 
