How unlucky am I, having to apologize for doing the right thing! <i>(giving</i> CORNWALL <i>a letter)</i> This is the letter he was talking about, and it confirms he was a spy for France. Oh God, I wish he had never betrayed us, or that I hadn't been the one to discover his treason.
 
