God willing, our love and our happiness will only increase as we get older.
 
--%%-- pageNum: 78 --%%--
 
Amen to that! I can't talk about my happiness anymore. It's too much. I hope these kisses I'm about to give you are the closest we ever come to fighting.<i>(they kiss)</i>
 
