<i>(to</i> EMILIA<i>)</i> Go do what you do best, madam. Leave us alone for our hanky-panky, and shut the door behind you. If somebody comes, give a shout. That's your <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tooltip-link"><span class="tooltip-css tooltip-background"><h4 class="semi-bold">job</h4><p>Othello implies that Emilia\'s job is to help men and women have illicit sex.</p></span>job</a>, your job. Go on, hurry!
 
