<i>(speaking so that only</i> LUCENTIO <i>can hear)</i> Indeed, master. Let's keep quiet and watch.
 
<i>(to</i> GREMIO <i>and</i> HORTENSIO<i>)</i> Gentlemen, since I'd like to make good on what I've said-Bianca, go inside. And don't be unhappy, my dear. Whatever happens, you know I'll never love you less.
 
What a spoiled little brat. She'd make herself cry now, if she could think of a reason.
 
