Shut up, monster.-Madame tree, is this jacket for me? Thank you kindly. The tree's lost its jacket. <i>(he takes a jacket hanging on the tree)-</i>Now the jacket might lose its fur trim and become a bald jacket. <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tooltip-link"><span class="tooltip-css tooltip-background"><h4 class="semi-bold"></h4><p>Stephano makes an elaborate (and untranslatable) pun about the shirt being like a sailor who goes to the tropics and gets a venereal disease.</p></span></a>
 
